                            <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>

                            <p>Welcome to Trustway Capital. Trustway Capital is a trailblazing financial and investment firm, committed to making investment an easy venture for our clients. Comprised of a team of seasoned financial experts and analysts, we help clients to spot and invest in the best deals available. Not only do we get you the best deals, we also ensure profitable returns on investment. Investment opportunities that we make available to our clients cuts across the global Financial Market, Agriculture, and Real Estate, to mention a few.</p>

                            <p>Your access to this website and App is subject to these Terms and Conditions, Trustway Capital’s Privacy Policy Statement, Notices, Disclaimers and any other terms and conditions or other statements contained on this website (referred to collectively as <strong>“Terms and Conditions or Terms”</strong>). By using this website and App you agree to be subject to the Terms and Conditions, and agreeing to comply with and be bound by the following Terms. You are advised to review the following Terms carefully. If you do not agree to these Terms, you should not use this website.</p>

                            <h3>Acceptance of Terms/Agreement</h3>

                            <p>You agree to the terms and conditions outlined in this Terms of Use Agreement ("Agreement") with respect to Trustway Capital website (the "website") and App. This Agreement constitutes the entire and only agreement between Trustway Capital and you, and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, representations, warranties and understandings with Trustway Capital, the content, products or services, trade deals provided by or through this website, and the subject matter of this Agreement. This Agreement may be amended at any time by us from time to time without specific notice to you. The latest Agreement will be posted on the website, and you should review this Agreement prior to using this website.</p>

                            <h3>General Terms</h3>

                            <p>You undertake to keep confidential all confidential information you have received from this website relating to your transaction or trade deals with us and to only use such confidential information to assess your possibility to participate in financing.
                            <br><br>
                            You understand and accept that making an investment with us through this website constitutes a binding legal agreement.
                            <br><br>
                            You make the investment and financing decision at your own discretion and are solely responsible for the decision you have made. Clients are advised to invest in Trustway Capital the amount they can afford to lose in the event of capital market failure or insolvency of investment.
                            <br><br>
                            You agree that transactions with Trustway Capital may involve Promissory Note, Bonds and other transaction modes as may be directed by Trustway Capital in relation to capital market transactions and trade deals.
                            <br><br>
                            There may be special legal requirements concerning investors in some states. It is your duty to make sure that such requirements are fulfilled. Trustway Capital has no obligation to check that the requirements are fulfilled.
                            <br><br>
                            You accept that Trustway Capital is not under any obligation to show any trading records or history to any individual, body, organisation or legal entity.</p>

                            <h3>Registering an Account</h3>

                            <p>When registering an account via this website or our App you warrant that all information you provide is true and accurate to the best of your knowledge and belief. We reserve the right to refuse to register any user or investor. You are solely responsible for protecting your login details and password and we will not be held liable for any loss or damage that may result from your failure to do so.</p>

                            <h3>Availability of the Website or App</h3>

                            <p>Trustway Capital will endeavour to keep this website or App up and running smoothly. However, Trustway Capital takes no responsibility for, and will not be liable for the website or App being temporarily unavailable due to technical issues beyond our control.</p>

                            <h3>Limited Right to Use</h3>

